  Eva, 47, dazzled in her glamorous white gown, which featured a sheer skirt. The skirt was bedazzled with sequins and accentuated her toned legs, as well as allowing her to show off her elegant silver stilettos. The bodice of the garment was covered in delicate white netting and featured a low-cut neckline with a strap covering one shoulder. The actress completed her look with some red lipstick and wore her hair in a ponytail.  